---
/**
 * Classic Bidvertiser banner (publisher 80833, feed 2106253). It renders
 * inline where placed, so it can appear more than once per page. The script
 * is parser-blocking (no async/defer) so its document.write runs during parse;
 * data-cfasync="false" stops Cloudflare Rocket Loader from deferring it, which
 * would otherwise break document.write.
 */
---

<div class="mx-auto my-8 flex w-full max-w-3xl justify-center" data-ad-placement="bidvertiser-banner">
  <script
    is:inline
    data-cfasync="false"
    src="//bdv.bidvertiser.com/BidVertiser.dbm?pid=80833&bid=2106253&fid=2106253"
    type="text/javascript"></script>
</div>
